  "markdown": "[Skip to main content](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/glossary#__docusaurus_skipToContent_fallback)\n[![Rigetti](https://docs.rigetti.com/img/rigetti.png)](https://docs.rigetti.com/)[QCS](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/)[Integration](https://docs.rigetti.com/integration/)\n[QCS Console](https://qcs.rigetti.com)\n`ctrl``K`\n  * [Welcome to Quantum Cloud Services](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/)\n  * [Getting Started](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/getting-started/)\n  * [Guides](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/guides/)\n  * [References](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/references/)\n  * [Troubleshooting](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/troubleshooting/)\n  * [Glossary](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/glossary)\n  * [FAQ](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/faq)\n\n\n  * [](https://docs.rigetti.com/)\n  * Glossary\n\n\nOn this page\n# Glossary\n### QPU Endpoint[\u200b](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/glossary#qpu-endpoint \"Direct link to QPU Endpoint\")\nA QPU Endpoint is a collection of services that enables users to run a job on a QPU.\n### Gateway[\u200b](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/glossary#gateway \"Direct link to Gateway\")\nA service that enables highly available on-demand access for running jobs on the QPU. See [QCS QPU Gateway](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/guides/access-a-qpu/qcs-qpu-gateway)\n### Compilation and Translation[\u200b](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/glossary#compilation-and-translation \"Direct link to Compilation and Translation\")\nWhen preparing a program to run on a QPU, it usually goes through two compilation steps. The first is `quilc`, the optimizing compiler. The second compiles your program down to the machine code needed to run your program on a QPU's control system. While these are both technically compilation steps, we've historically referred to the latter as \"translation\" to differentiate it from `quilc` compilation. See [How Programs Are Built & Run](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/guides/how-programs-are-built-and-run)for more details on these compilation steps.\n[Previous Report an Issue](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/troubleshooting/report-an-issue)[Next FAQ](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/faq)\n  * [QPU Endpoint](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/glossary#qpu-endpoint)\n  * [Gateway](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/glossary#gateway)\n  * [Compilation and Translation](https://docs.rigetti.com/qcs/glossary#compilation-and-translation)\n\n\nCopyright \u00a9 2026 Rigetti Computing.\n",
